              "content": "Good progress! Now comparing with expected:\n\n**Matches perfectly:**\n- W1de自摸: ✅ `300・500以上`\n- W1de荣和 from all 3: ✅ `1000以上`\n- W1de放铳: ✅ `16000以下`, `5800以下`, `12000以下`\n- 被Lemontruth自摸: ✅ `6000・12000以下`\n- 被浅梦自摸: ✅ `4000・8000以下`\n- 被kagayaki亲家自摸: ✅ `6000all以下`\n- Lemontruth自摸: ✅ `300・500以上`\n- Lemontruth荣和: ✅ `1000以上` for all\n- Lemontruth放铳 to W1de: ✅ `6400以下`\n- Lemontruth放铳 to 浅梦: ✅ `3200以下`\n- kagayaki自摸: ✅ `8000all以上`\n- kagayaki荣和: ✅ `18000以上`, `24000以上`, `36000以上`\n- 流局分支: ✅ all 16 match\n\n**Differences to fix:**\n\n1. **W1de danger zones**: \n   - Expected: `Lemontruth点浅梦 24000以上会丢晋级资格` — MISSING\n   - Expected: `Lemontruth点kagayaki 24000以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格` — different\n   - Got: `Lemontruth点kagayaki 64000以上` — wrong\n   - Expected: `浅梦点kagayaki 24000以上3倍役满以下` — different\n   - Got: `浅梦点kagayaki 12000以上` — different\n   - Expected: `kagayaki点Lemontruth 役満以上3倍役满以下`\n   - Got: `kagayaki点Lemontruth 36000以上`\n   - Expected: `kagayaki点浅梦 8000以上3倍役满以下`\n   - Got: `kagayaki点浅梦 36000以上`\n\n2. **Lemontruth放铳 to 浅梦**: Expected has `对浅梦放铳 役満`, got `对浅梦放铳 32000以上32000以下`\n\n3. **Lemontruth放铳 to kagayaki**: Expected `18000以下`, got `18000以下` ✅\n\n4. **被W1de自摸**: Expected `300・500以上`, got `任意点数` (different)\n\n5. **被kagayaki亲家自摸**: Expected `500all以上`, got `任意点数` (different)\n\n6. **浅梦 conditions**: \n   - Lemontruth荣和: Expected `3900以上`, got `3400以上`\n   - kagayaki荣和: Expected `12000以上`, got `12000以上` ✅\n   - 被Lemontruth自摸: Expected `役満以上`, got `8000・16000以上`\n\n7. **浅梦 danger zones**: Expected has many entries, got none\n\n8. **kagayaki danger zones**: Expected has many entries, got none\n\nThe main issues are:\n\n**Issue A**: The danger zone calculation. Looking at expected output for `kagayaki点浅梦 8000以上3倍役满以下` — kagayaki is dealer (北), so ronning 浅梦 uses DEALER_RON values. In DEALER_RON, 8000 is not present. The expected uses child-equivalent labeling... \n\nWait, I think I see it now. Let me check: \"kagayaki点浅梦\" — the expected says `8000以上`. In my DEALER_RON list, the scores near 8000 are: 7700, 8700. So 8000 is not a valid dealer ron. But if we map it to the child equivalent: mangan (child) = 8000.\n\nI think the expected output is using **child ron values** as the universal display format, regardless of who the attacker is. The idea is: \"what hand level does the attacker need?\" Since mangan is mangan regardless of dealer/child, the threshold is shown in child-equivalent values. The system still calculates with the correct dealer/child amounts, but displays using child-scale labels.\n\n**Actually, I think the simpler explanation is**: the danger zone is calculated differently. Maybe it's checking scores from the **VICTIM's perspective** (what the victim loses), and child ron values are used because the victim is a child. When kagayaki (dealer) rons 浅梦 (child), 浅梦 loses dealer-level points. But the display shows child-level equivalents.\n\nHmm, that still doesn't make 8000 appear for a dealer ron scenario.\n\nLet me try yet another interpretation: **the danger zone just uses CHILD_RON values for everyone** as a simplified check. Mangan for child = 8000, and when dealer rons, they actually get MORE than the listed amount (dealer mangan = 12000 vs child 8000). So the check becomes: \"if the transfer amount is child-scale 8000 or more...\"\n\nLet me verify: W1de current=48200, Lemontruth=13300, 浅梦=20000, kagayaki(dealer)=18500.\nPre-PT: W1de=-46.5, Lemontruth=63.1, 浅梦=9.8, kagayaki=-26.4.\n\nFor `kagayaki点浅梦`, using CHILD_RON:\n- If score = 8000 (child mangan): kagayaki gains 8000+0=8000+kyotaku*1000=8000, 浅梦 loses 8000\n  - kagayaki: 18500+8000=26500, 浅梦: 20000-8000=12000\n  - kagayaki pt: (26500-30000)/1000 + (-26.4) + uma = -3.5 + (-26.4) + uma\n  - W1de: 48200 → pt = 18.2 + (-46.5) + uma\n  - Lemontruth: 13300 → pt = -16.7 + 63.1 + uma\n  - 浅梦: 12000 → pt = -18.0 + 9.8 + uma\n  \n  Rankings by score: W1de(48200) > kagayaki(26500) > Lemontruth(13300) > 浅梦(12000)\n  Uma: W1de=+50, kagayaki=+10, Lemontruth=-10, 浅梦=-30\n\n  Final PT:\n  - W1de: -46.5 + 18.2 + 50 = 21.7\n  - kagayaki: -26.4 + (-3.5) + 10 = -19.9\n  - Lemontruth: 63.1 + (-16.7) + (-10) = 36.4\n  - 浅梦: 9.8 + (-18.0) + (-30) = -38.2\n\n  Ranked by pt: Lemontruth(36.4) > W1de(21.7) > kagayaki(-19.9) > 浅梦(-38.2)\n  W1de is 2nd → qualifies (top 2). ✅ Still qualifies.\n\nHmm wait, but the expected says \"8000以上...会丢晋级资格\". So at 8000, W1de should LOSE qualification. Let me re-check...\n\nActually the danger zone is from W1de's perspective. The W1de block says:\n```\nW1de危险区间:\nkagayaki点浅梦\t8000以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格\n```\n\nThis means: if kagayaki rons 浅梦 for 8000 or more (up to 3倍役满), W1de loses promotion.\n\nBut my calculation above shows W1de still qualifies at 8000... unless the scores being used are different.\n\nLet me re-check using DEALER_RON since kagayaki IS the dealer:\n- If kagayaki (dealer) rons 浅梦 for dealer mangan = 12000:\n  - kagayaki: 18500+12000=30500, 浅梦: 20000-12000=8000\n  - Rankings: W1de(48200), kagayaki(30500), Lemontruth(13300), 浅梦(8000)\n  - Uma: W1de=+50, kagayaki=+10, Lemontruth=-10, 浅梦=-30\n  - W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n  - kagayaki pt: -26.4+0.5+10 = -15.9\n  - Lemontruth pt: 63.1-16.7-10 = 36.4\n  - 浅梦 pt: 9.8-22+(-30) = -42.2\n  \n  W1de still 2nd (21.7 > -15.9). ✅ Still qualifies.\n\n- If kagayaki (dealer) rons 浅梦 for 18000 (haneman):\n  - kagayaki: 36500, 浅梦: 2000\n  - Rankings: W1de(48200), kagayaki(36500), Lemontruth(13300), 浅梦(2000)\n  - Uma: W1de=+50, kagayaki=+10, Lemontruth=-10, 浅梦=-30\n  - W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n  - kagayaki pt: -26.4+6.5+10 = -9.9\n  - Still W1de > kagayaki. ✅\n\n- If kagayaki (dealer) rons 浅梦 for 24000 (baiman):\n  - kagayaki: 42500, 浅梦: -4000\n  - Rankings: W1de(48200), kagayaki(42500), Lemontruth(13300), 浅梦(-4000)\n  - Uma: W1de=+50, kagayaki=+10, Lemontruth=-10, 浅梦=-30\n  - W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n  - kagayaki pt: -26.4+12.5+10 = -3.9\n  - Still W1de qualifies (2nd). ✅\n\n- If kagayaki (dealer) rons 浅梦 for 36000 (sanbaiman):\n  - kagayaki: 54500, 浅梦: -16000\n  - Rankings: kagayaki(54500), W1de(48200), Lemontruth(13300), 浅梦(-16000)\n  - Uma: kagayaki=+50, W1de=+10, Lemontruth=-10, 浅梦=-30\n  - W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+10 = -18.3\n  - kagayaki pt: -26.4+24.5+50 = 48.1\n  - Lemontruth pt: 63.1-16.7-10 = 36.4\n  - Ranked: kagayaki(48.1) > Lemontruth(36.4) > W1de(-18.3) > 浅梦(-64.2)\n  - W1de is 3rd → does NOT qualify (top 2). ❌ Lost!\n\nSo with DEALER_RON, the threshold is at 36000 (sanbaiman) for kagayaki点浅梦. My output says `36000以上` which is correct for DEALER_RON.\n\nBut the expected says `8000以上3倍役满以下`. This doesn't match with dealer scoring.\n\nUnless... the expected output is computing with CHILD_RON for ALL scenarios in the danger zone. Let me check with CHILD_RON 8000:\n- kagayaki: 18500+8000=26500, 浅梦: 20000-8000=12000\n- W1de pt: 21.7 (as calculated above) → still qualifies\n\nSo with child 8000, W1de still qualifies. The expected output must be wrong, or I'm misunderstanding something fundamental about how \"点\" works here.\n\nOH WAIT. I just realized: maybe \"kagayaki点浅梦\" means **浅梦 rons kagayaki**, not kagayaki rons 浅梦! In Chinese mahjong terminology, \"A点B\" could mean \"A deals in to B\" (A is the victim/feeder). Let me re-read...\n\nLooking at the 晋级条件 section:\n```\n对Lemontruth放铳\t16000以下\n```\n\"对A放铳\" = \"deal in to A\" = you are the victim, A wins.\n\nAnd danger zone:\n```\nLemontruth点浅梦\t24000以上会丢晋级资格\n```\n\n\"A点B\" — in Chinese, \"点\" (diǎn) can mean \"to deal in to\" (放铳). So \"Lemontruth点浅梦\" = Lemontruth deals in to 浅梦 = **浅梦 rons from Lemontruth**.\n\nLet me verify: `Lemontruth点浅梦 24000以上`:\n- 浅梦 (child) rons Lemontruth for 24000 (sanbaiman)\n- 浅梦: 20000+24000=44000, Lemontruth: 13300-24000=-10700\n- Rankings: W1de(48200), 浅梦(44000), kagayaki(18500), Lemontruth(-10700)\n- Uma: W1de=+50, 浅梦=+10, kagayaki=-10, Lemontruth=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1-40.7-30 = -7.6\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8+14+10 = 33.8\n- kagayaki pt: -26.4-11.5-10 = -47.9\n- Ranked: 浅梦(33.8) > W1de(21.7) > Lemontruth(-7.6) > kagayaki(-47.9)\n- W1de is 2nd → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 32000 (yakuman):\n- 浅梦: 52000, Lemontruth: -18700\n- Rankings: 浅梦(52000), W1de(48200), kagayaki(18500), Lemontruth(-18700)\n- Uma: 浅梦=+50, W1de=+10, kagayaki=-10, Lemontruth=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+10 = -18.3\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1-48.7-30 = -15.6\n- Ranked: 浅梦(41.8) > Lemontruth(-15.6) > W1de(-18.3) > kagayaki(-47.9)\n- W1de is 3rd → does NOT qualify ❌\n\nSo the danger starts at child yakuman (32000) when Lemontruth deals to 浅梦? But expected says 24000.\n\nLet me recheck at 24000:\n- 浅梦: 20000+24000=44000, Lemontruth: 13300-24000=-10700\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+(-10700-30000)/1000+(-30) = 63.1-40.7-30 = -7.6\n- Wait, Lemontruth score is -10700. (-10700-30000)/1000 = -40.7. Plus pre-pt 63.1 plus uma -30 = -7.6\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8+(44000-30000)/1000+10 = 9.8+14+10 = 33.8\n- kagayaki pt: -26.4+(18500-30000)/1000+(-10) = -26.4-11.5-10 = -47.9\n- Rankings: 浅梦(33.8) > W1de(21.7) > Lemontruth(-7.6) > kagayaki(-47.9)\n- W1de is 2nd → still qualifies ✅\n\nSo at 24000, W1de still qualifies. The danger should NOT start at 24000 for Lemontruth点浅梦...\n\nUnless I'm wrong about \"A点B\" meaning \"A deals to B\". Let me consider the opposite: \"A点B\" = \"A rons B\" = A is the winner.\n\n`Lemontruth点浅梦 24000以上`:\n- Lemontruth (child) rons 浅梦 for 24000:\n- Lemontruth: 13300+24000=37300, 浅梦: 20000-24000=-4000\n- Rankings: W1de(48200), Lemontruth(37300), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-4000)\n- Uma: W1de=+50, Lemontruth=+10, kagayaki=-10, 浅梦=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+7.3+10 = 80.4\n- kagayaki pt: -26.4-11.5-10 = -47.9\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8-34-30 = -54.2\n- Ranked: Lemontruth(80.4) > W1de(21.7) > kagayaki(-47.9) > 浅梦(-54.2)\n- W1de is 2nd → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 32000 (yakuman):\n- Lemontruth: 45300, 浅梦: -12000\n- Rankings: W1de(48200), Lemontruth(45300), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-12000)\n- Uma: W1de=+50, Lemontruth=+10, kagayaki=-10, 浅梦=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+15.3+10 = 88.4\n- W1de is 2nd → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 64000 (double yakuman):\n- Lemontruth: 77300, 浅梦: -44000\n- Rankings: Lemontruth(77300), W1de(48200), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-44000)\n- Uma: Lemontruth=+50, W1de=+10, kagayaki=-10, 浅梦=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+10 = -18.3\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+47.3+50 = 160.4\n- kagayaki pt: -26.4-11.5-10 = -47.9\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8-74-30 = -94.2\n- Ranked: Lemontruth(160.4) > W1de(-18.3) > kagayaki(-47.9) > 浅梦(-94.2)\n- W1de is 2nd → qualifies ✅\n\nHmm, W1de qualifies even with double yakuman... So \"Lemontruth点浅梦\" shouldn't cause W1de to lose qualification at any level? That contradicts the expected output which says \"24000以上会丢晋级资格\".\n\nWait, let me re-read the expected output more carefully:\n\n```\nW1de危险区间:\nLemontruth点浅梦\t24000以上会丢晋级资格\nLemontruth点kagayaki\t24000以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格\n浅梦点kagayaki\t24000以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格\nkagayaki点Lemontruth\t役満以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格\nkagayaki点浅梦\t8000以上3倍役满以下会丢晋级资格\n```\n\nOK so for \"Lemontruth点浅梦 24000以上\", maybe this IS \"Lemontruth deals in to 浅梦\" = 浅梦 wins from Lemontruth. Let me check more carefully.\n\nWhen 浅梦(child) rons Lemontruth for 24000 (sanbaiman):\nRankings: W1de(48200), 浅梦(44000), kagayaki(18500), Lemontruth(-10700)\n- W1de: 1st → uma +50 → pt = -46.5 + 18.2 + 50 = 21.7\n- 浅梦: 2nd → uma +10 → pt = 9.8 + 14 + 10 = 33.8\n- kagayaki: 3rd → uma -10 → pt = -26.4 - 11.5 - 10 = -47.9\n- Lemontruth: 4th → uma -30 → pt = 63.1 - 40.7 - 30 = -7.6\n\nTop 2 by pt: 浅梦(33.8) > W1de(21.7) → W1de IS 2nd, qualifies. ✅\n\nSo W1de does NOT lose qualification. The expected output saying 24000 is wrong? Or my understanding of the scoring is wrong?\n\nLet me re-examine the M-League oka. In M-League:\n- Start: 25000\n- Return: 30000\n- The difference is 5000 per player = 20000 total goes to the 1st place as \"oka\"\n\nWait, that's important! **Oka**: (30000 - 25000) × 4 = 20000 goes to 1st place. So the 1st place uma should actually be +50 INCLUDING the oka, OR the oka is separate.\n\nLooking at the M-League rule:\n> 持ち点は、30,000点を超える得点をプラス（＋）、不足する失点をマイナス（▲）とする。\n> 順位点: 1位＋50,000点　2位+10,000点　3位▲10,000点　4位▲30,000点\n\nSo the calculation is:\n1. Subtract 30000 (return point) from each player's score → base pt\n2. Add uma/順位点 based on rank\n\nThis means the total base pt = (sum of scores - 120000) / 1000. If all players start with 25000, total = 100000. So base pt total = (100000-120000)/1000 = -20. Uma total = 50+10-10-30 = 20. So everything balances to 0 when scores total to 100000.\n\nBUT, with kyotaku on the table, the total scores might not be 100000. If there are 2 kyotaku (2000 pts on table), total in-play = 98000.\n\nOK so my calculation seems correct. Let me re-verify the example case:\n- Scores: W1de=48200, Lemontruth=13300, 浅梦=20000, kagayaki=18500\n- Total = 100000 ✅ (kyotaku=0)\n- Pre-pts: -46.5, 63.1, 9.8, -26.4\n\nAfter 浅梦 rons Lemontruth for 24000 (child sanbaiman):\n- W1de=48200, Lemontruth=-10700, 浅梦=44000, kagayaki=18500\n- Rankings by score: W1de(1st), 浅梦(2nd), kagayaki(3rd), Lemontruth(4th)\n- Base pt: (48200-30000)/1000=18.2, (-10700-30000)/1000=-40.7, (44000-30000)/1000=14, (18500-30000)/1000=-11.5\n- Uma: 50, -10, 10, -30 (wrong, let me re-sort)\n\nWait, I need to assign uma by ranking:\n1st = W1de → +50\n2nd = 浅梦 → +10  \n3rd = kagayaki → -10\n4th = Lemontruth → -30\n\nFinal pt:\n- W1de: -46.5 + 18.2 + 50 = 21.7\n- 浅梦: 9.8 + 14 + 10 = 33.8\n- kagayaki: -26.4 + (-11.5) + (-10) = -47.9\n- Lemontruth: 63.1 + (-40.7) + (-30) = -7.6\n\nTop 2 by final pt: 浅梦(33.8), W1de(21.7) → W1de qualifies. ✅\n\nLet me try 浅梦 rons Lemontruth for 32000 (yakuman):\n- Lemontruth: 13300-32000=-18700, 浅梦: 20000+32000=52000\n- Rankings: 浅梦(52000), W1de(48200), kagayaki(18500), Lemontruth(-18700)\n- Uma: 浅梦=+50, W1de=+10, kagayaki=-10, Lemontruth=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5 + 18.2 + 10 = -18.3\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8 + 22 + 50 = 81.8\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1 - 48.7 - 30 = -15.6\n- kagayaki pt: -26.4 - 11.5 - 10 = -47.9\n\nTop 2: 浅梦(81.8), W1de(-18.3)?? Wait...\nLemontruth pt = -15.6, W1de pt = -18.3. So Lemontruth(-15.6) > W1de(-18.3).\n\nTop 2 by final pt: 浅梦(81.8), Lemontruth(-15.6) → W1de is 3rd → does NOT qualify ❌\n\nSo the threshold for `Lemontruth点浅梦` (浅梦 winning) should be at 32000 (yakuman), not 24000!\n\nBut expected says 24000. Let me check if \"A点B\" means \"A rons FROM B\" = \"A wins from B\":\n\n`Lemontruth点浅梦` = Lemontruth rons 浅梦 (Lemontruth wins):\n- Lemontruth: 13300+24000=37300, 浅梦: 20000-24000=-4000\n- Rankings: W1de(48200), Lemontruth(37300), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-4000)\n- Uma: W1de=+50, Lemontruth=+10, kagayaki=-10, 浅梦=-30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+50 = 21.7\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+7.3+10 = 80.4\n- W1de is 2nd → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 32000:\n- Lemontruth: 45300, 浅梦: -12000\n- Rankings: W1de(48200), Lemontruth(45300), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-12000)\n- Uma: +50, +10, -10, -30\n- W1de pt: 21.7 → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 64000:\n- Lemontruth: 77300, 浅梦: -44000\n- Rankings: Lemontruth(77300), W1de(48200), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-44000)\n- Uma: +50, +10, -10, -30\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+10 = -18.3\n- Lemontruth pt: 63.1+47.3+50 = 160.4\n- kagayaki pt: -47.9\n- 浅梦 pt: 9.8-74-30 = -94.2\n- Top 2: Lemontruth(160.4), W1de(-18.3) → qualifies ✅\n\nAt 96000 (triple yakuman):\n- Lemontruth: 109300, 浅梦: -76000\n- Rankings: Lemontruth(109300), W1de(48200), kagayaki(18500), 浅梦(-76000)\n- W1de pt: -46.5+18.2+10 = -18.3, still 2nd by pt ✅\n\nSo with \"Lemontruth rons 浅梦\", W1de never loses qualification! That contradicts the expected output.\n\nOK, there must be a different interpretation. Let me re-read the expected output ONE MORE TIME:\n\n```\nW1de危险区间:\nLemontruth点浅梦\t24000以上会丢晋级资格\n```\n\nWhat if \"点\" really means \"rons\"... and what I'm calculating is correct but there's a DIFFERENT rule about how pt is computed? Let me re-check if there's oka handling I'm missing.\n\nThe M-League example from the rules page:\n> 35,800点の2位→+5.8p+10.0p(順位点)=+15.8p\n> 41,600点の1位→+11.6p+50.0p（順位点）=+61.6p\n\nSo 35800 - 30000 = 5800 → 5.8p. Yes, my calculation is right.\n